u != 0; marked 'deg').  Pair features: [K_q, K_q', K_q*K_q'] (product
by twisted multiplicativity).  DISCLOSED LIMITS: census phases are
heavily clustered (mirror orbits) -- several K_q have little or no
variance across the 12 windows; fits carry the design-matrix rank;
n = 12 (10 small-clock pairs) or n = 6 (pairs with 19) against 4
parameters inflates R^2.  Tabulation only.

